These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, snowboarding
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, spinach
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
2 different games are played: backgammon, canasta
1. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Sport      | snowboarding     | soccer      |
| Food          | spinach | broccoli    |
| Hobby         | chess   | board-games |
| Game   | backgammon  | canasta      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
2 different games are played: billiard, bridge
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daisy
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
3. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
4. the person who growsdahlia is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Hobby       | filmmaking         | woodworking |
| Game         | bridge | billiard   |
| Flower   | dahlia               | daisy  |

