.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
City: boston, hamburg
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, japanese
There 2 different types of food: orange, cabbage
1. the australian is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is not to the right of the person eating cabbage##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| City   | boston       | hamburg |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese |
| Food           | orange        | cabbage   |

