The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, nurse
There are 2 different nationalities: german, polish
There 2 different types of food: banana, tomato
1. the german is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
2. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the person eating tomato##8
3. the person eating tomato is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Pet         | frog | lizard  |
| Job           | nurse  | designer |
| Nationality   | polish | german   |
| Food     | tomato   | banana |

